members.name: onCommand
members.comment: Executes the given command, returning its success. If false is returned, then the "usage" plugin.yml entry for this command (if defined) will be sent to the player.

param: label - Alias of the command which was used
return: true if a valid command, otherwise false

name: org.bukkit.command.CommandExecutor
comment: Represents a class which contains a single method for executing commands
